eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.ckan

Class CkanGroupStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.ckan.CkanGroupStructure
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CkanGroup, CkanOrganization

    public abstract class CkanGroupStructure
extends Object
    This abstract class models the same data structure that Ckan uses for both groups and organizations. Since they are different things and work with different APIs we made two different implementations. For groups use CkanGroup and organizations use CkanOrganization (Ckan way to tell the difference is the isOrganization() field).
    Author:
    David Leoni
